WEBVTT

00:00:29.473 --> 00:00:33.417
starting with Bill Gates,
Susan Cain, Tim Ferris.

00:00:33.822 --> 00:00:37.222
But this episode is a tasty appetizer.

00:00:37.895 --> 00:00:42.085
It was recorded live at the TED conference
that we just held in Vancouver.

00:00:42.514 --> 00:00:45.242
I sat down with Roger McNamee,

00:00:45.266 --> 00:00:48.927
who's been an influential voice
in technology for many years,

00:00:48.951 --> 00:00:51.070
been coming to TED
for many years, actually.

00:00:51.094 --> 00:00:52.292
But recently,

00:00:52.316 --> 00:00:56.387
he has turned into an outspoken critic
of some of the big tech companies.

00:00:56.831 --> 00:01:00.751
In fact, this spring, he published
a searing critique of Facebook